steps.description:
Create a `config.troy` file:
```troy
define flow main
flow
  use tremor::connectors;
  define connector input from connectors::stdio
  with
    codec = "json"
  end;
  define connector output from connectors::stdio
  with
    codec = "json"
  end;
  define pipeline passthrough
  pipeline
    select event from in into out;
  end;
  create connector input;
  create connector output;
  create pipeline passthrough;
  connect /connector/input to /pipeline/passthrough;
  connect /pipeline/passthrough to /connector/output;
end;
deploy flow main;
```
Run the pipeline:
```bash
tremor run config.troy
```
